do with these Lil Galleries.

00:36:40.180 --> 00:36:41.680
Is online now, at
Lil Galleries.com,

00:36:41.680 --> 00:36:46.420
but it's these
combinations of voice.

00:36:46.420 --> 00:36:48.150
Photographs contain your voice.

00:36:48.150 --> 00:36:50.040
In my case, I just
happened to have a voice

00:36:50.040 --> 00:36:51.670
that I use as a voice.

00:36:51.670 --> 00:36:53.780
And I wondered what would
happen if I put them

00:36:53.780 --> 00:36:57.640
together and created a
third way of speaking

00:36:57.640 --> 00:36:59.910
through these videos.

00:36:59.910 --> 00:37:01.760
So what if?

00:37:01.760 --> 00:37:03.200
What if you did that?

00:37:03.200 --> 00:37:08.360
What if you took-- I
don't know, a photograph.

00:37:08.360 --> 00:37:10.840
What if you took
this photograph?

00:37:10.840 --> 00:37:14.260
