00:37:24.330 --> 00:37:26.359
And you look at that
and you go, wow.

00:37:26.359 --> 00:37:27.400
That is really something.

00:37:27.400 --> 00:37:29.620
That house has a story to tell.

00:37:29.620 --> 00:37:33.740
Nice telephone lines, by the
way, it's really awesome.

00:37:33.740 --> 00:37:37.100
And it's got some cool colors.

00:37:37.100 --> 00:37:38.530
Now, I see it in
black and white,

00:37:38.530 --> 00:37:39.680
