00:37:42.020 --> 00:37:47.620
And I said, what if this is in
a transit place, this house?

00:37:47.620 --> 00:37:52.490
What if we made it in a
transit place in its own world?

00:37:52.490 --> 00:37:55.520
And what if the light
were shining on it

00:37:55.520 --> 00:38:00.630
