and telling its story?

00:38:00.630 --> 00:38:06.660
And what if it were
black and white?

00:38:06.660 --> 00:38:08.870
It's off the screen.

00:38:08.870 --> 00:38:13.326
That becomes another story--
another way to tell the story.

00:38:13.326 --> 00:38:15.700
