different story?

00:38:41.480 --> 00:38:44.730
That's just me playing
my what if game one day.

00:38:44.730 --> 00:38:48.180
But that what if, and
then taking the action.

00:38:48.180 --> 00:38:50.610
So now we're signature,
we're art and dreaming,

00:38:50.610 --> 00:38:54.200
