00:50:09.870 --> 00:50:12.560
have to say, what your
stand is going to be,

00:50:12.560 --> 00:50:14.977
what mark you're going to
leave, what people are going

00:50:14.977 --> 00:50:17.060
to say about you and think
about when you're gone.

00:50:17.060 --> 00:50:19.040
Not just from the room,
but from this life.

00:50:19.040 --> 00:50:20.770
Is it going to be different?

00:50:20.770 --> 00:50:23.260
Or is it just going to be
the same old, same old?

