I get caught in the same
thing everybody else does.

00:50:25.390 --> 00:50:29.190
I work off a list,
which is stupid.

00:50:29.190 --> 00:50:31.820
But at the same time, I go,
all right, I've got a list.

00:50:31.820 --> 00:50:33.860
But what does it mean?

00:50:33.860 --> 00:50:36.161
What are the things
that I want to do

00:50:36.161 --> 00:50:37.660
that are going to
make a difference?

