I can bitch and moan
and whine and complain

00:50:41.980 --> 00:50:43.934
better than probably
any of you in here.

00:50:43.934 --> 00:50:44.975
Because I got some drama.

00:50:47.690 --> 00:50:48.870
I got some juice behind it.

00:50:48.870 --> 00:50:49.890
But why?

00:50:49.890 --> 00:50:51.290
What's the point?

00:50:51.290 --> 00:50:53.980
And when it comes photography,
